---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="PCA on Marketing Surveys">
  <section class="py-24 px-6 fade-in">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">PCA on Marketing Surveys</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mb-4">
      This project applied dimensionality reduction using Principal Component Analysis to a high-dimensional marketing survey dataset with 100+ behavioral questions.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-primary-dark">
      <li>Performed hybrid deletion + imputation for missing values</li>
      <li>Standardized features and performed PCA using scikit-learn</li>
      <li>Visualized explained variance and identified 5 core latent factors</li>
      <li>Used K-means clustering on reduced data for customer segmentation</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
